title: Police investigating Interstate 84 crash near Flying Wye
title_page: Police investigating Interstate 84 crash near Flying Wye
maintext:
A crash on eastbound Interstate 84 just before the Flying Wye that was blocking the left lane is now cleared, according to Idaho State Police.
Idaho State Police were investigating the crash Monday morning at milepost 48.5.
